# ==============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ==============================================================================
#
# GENERATION COMMANDS:
# - API Keys (64 hex chars): openssl rand -hex 32
# - Tokens (base64): openssl rand -base64 48
# - JWT Secrets: openssl rand -hex 64
# - Fernet Keys: python -c "from cryptography.fernet import Fernet; print(Fernet.generate_key().decode())"
#
# PERMISSIONS:
# Set strict permissions on this file:
#   chmod 600 secrets.env
#   chown root:root secrets.env  # or appropriate user
#
# ROTATION POLICY:
# - Rotate all keys quarterly
# - Rotate immediately if compromised
# - Keep audit log of all rotations
# - Test key rotation in staging first
#
# SECRETS MANAGEMENT:
# For production, use external secrets managers:
# - HashiCorp Vault: https://www.vaultproject.io/
# - AWS Secrets Manager: https://aws.amazon.com/secrets-manager/
# - Azure Key Vault: https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/key-vault/
# - Google Secret Manager: https://cloud.google.com/secret-manager
#
# ENVIRONMENT-SPECIFIC:
# Maintain separate secrets.env files for each environment:
# - secrets.dev.env (development)
# - secrets.staging.env (staging)
# - secrets.prod.env (production)
#
# ==============================================================================
